title: 'Pathetic Amazon experience!! quality assurance is not upto mark'
body: Got damaged product and can't get a refund or replacement!! bought 10 lakh+ worth of products from amazon never had an issue but I can't take this... money is money I can't accept damaged product with no refund... about product its nice but mainly for girls it got feminine smell not upto the mark!!! if you want to smell like flowers buy this!
